These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, funk
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, collecting, gardening, magic-tricks
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, pink, lilac, white
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the fan of classical##6
5. the person who likes lilac is not the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##6
6. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
7. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the fan of disco and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
8. the person who likes light-blue is between the fan of country and the fan of disco##2
9. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | funk      | country   | classical  |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks    | gardening   | reading | collecting  |
| Color         | white | light-blue | lilac     | pink |

