.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose, begonia, poppy
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, nigerian, russian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, february, october, june
1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
2. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
4. the american is between the russian and the person who growsbegonia##2
5. the person who growsbegonia is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
6. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere between the person who growsrose and the dutch##7
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Flower         | poppy | begonia  | rose  | marigold |
| Nationality   | dutch   | nigerian | american | russian     |
| Birthday     | june    | april     | february     | october         |

