.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, gospel, jazz, salsa
City: berlin, marseilles, colone, hannover
House: modern, colonial, tower, wooden
1. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is the colonial house##1
3. the modern house is on the right of the colonial house##1
4. the fan of gospel is the colonial house##1
5. the person traveling to colone is the fan of salsa##1
6. the person traveling to berlin is the modern house##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
8. the wooden house is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of jazz##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | blues     | salsa   | jazz      |
| City   | marseilles    | berlin | colone | hannover  |
| House     | colonial | modern  | wooden    | tower |

