.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, october, march
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, paramedic, scientist, security-guard
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, mouse, rabbit
1. the person who's birthday is in september is not the security-guard##6
2. the paramedic is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the musician##7
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the paramedic and the person who's birthday is in february##7
5. the person who's birthday is in february is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the musician is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Birthday      | february  | september | october | march |
| Job   | security-guard | scientist  | paramedic  | musician    |
| Pet           | rabbit | cat  | horse    | mouse    |

