.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, lemonade, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, helicopter, bus
City: paris, prague, hannover, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
3. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
4. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the helicopter##7
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
8. the person drinking lemonade is not the person traveling to paris##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk     | lemonade | 7up        | fanta       |
| Transport         | helicopter | boat    | jet-ski | bus |
| City   | boston     | prague  | paris    | hannover   |

