4. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
5. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
7. the musician is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of funk##7
8. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
