.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, classical, indie, country
4 different games are played: chess, domino, bridge, canasta
4 different pets are kept: fish, hedgehog, lizard, rat
 1. the owner of the lizard is the fan of classical##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the fan of country##1
 3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
 4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 5. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 7. the person playing chess is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person playing canasta##7
 8. the fan of indie is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
10. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | funk | classical      | indie | country |
| Game   | bridge     | domino | chess  | canasta       |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard       | fish    | hedgehog  |

