4. the fan of ambient is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the prince-smoker##7
5. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
6. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
8. the owner of the dog is on the left of the fan of indie##1
9. the owner of the goat is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar          | havana  | davidoff  | prince | bolivar   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | ambient | indie     | techno   |
