 1. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing billiard is between the ranch-style house and the cape-cod house##2
 5. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 7. the ranch-style house is not the person drinking fanta##6
 8. the person playing chess is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 9. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
10. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing chess##1
11. the art-deco house is between the cape-cod house and the ranch-style house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | sprite     | fanta      | milk     |
